msgid "4500:[name]梨深[line]「ごめんね、タク。騙すようなことしちゃって」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]梨深[line]Sorry, Taku. I didn't mean to lie to you like this.[%p]"

msgid "4600:[name]七海[line]「梨深さんは謝らなくてもいいの。おにぃが超鈍感なのが悪いんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "4600:[name]七海[line]You don't need to apologize, Rimi. It's my brother's fault for being so clueless![%p]"

msgid "4700:がっくりとその場に膝をつく。[linebreak]してやられたという悔しさ。僕が本気で心配していたのをバカにするような言い草。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:I dropped to my knees right there. I felt frustrated at being tricked. I felt angry that she was making fun of me for being worried.[%p]"

msgid "4800:気に入らない。七海のやり方はホントに気に入らない。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:I didn't like it. I didn't like what Nanami had done at all.[%p]"

msgid "4900:でも、それ以上に。[linebreak]僕の心配が杞憂で終わったこと。[linebreak]七海は無事で、いたってピンピンしてること。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:But more than that... I'd been worried about nothing. Nanami was just fine. She wasn't hurt.[%p]"

msgid "5000:そのことへの安堵感の方が強くて、緊張の糸がぷっつりと切れた。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:Knowing that made me feel so relieved, like all the tension that had been building up inside me had just disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]梨深[line]「タク、大丈夫？」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]梨深[line]Taku, you okay?[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]七海[line]「おにぃ、落ち込んでないで、ほら、立って」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]七海[line]Come on, Brother. Don't be glum. Stand up.[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]七海[line]「これからお父さんとお母さんに、梨深さんを紹介しに行かなくちゃいけないんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]七海[line]You have to go introduce Rimi to Mom and Dad now.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]七海[line]「３人で一緒に、帰ろ！」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]七海[line]Let's all go together![%p]"

msgid "5500:ホントに、七海は生意気な妹だ。[linebreak]いつもいつも兄のことをバカにして。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:Nanami really was a huge brat. She was always making fun of her big brother.[%p]"

msgid "5600:僕は少し拗ねながら、仕方なく立ち上がる。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:I stood up, a little reluctantly, and with a small pouting look on my face.[%p]"

msgid "5700:梨深と七海が、楽しそうに笑い合って、僕の手を左右から握ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:Nanami and Rimi smiled at each other. One took my left hand, and another my right.[%p]"

msgid "5800:２人に手を引かれて、歩き出す。[linebreak]楽しくなりそうな予感。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:The two of them pulled me along as we started to walk. I could feel like my life was about to change for the better.[%p]"

msgid "5900:平和で、明るい未来が待っていそうな、そんな気がした――[%p]"
msgstr "5900:A peaceful, bright future was awaiting me.[%p]"

msgid "6000:突如――[%p]"
msgstr "6000:And suddenly...[%p]"

msgid "6100:甲高い音が耳に突き刺さった。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:A high-pitched sound stabbed my ears.[%p]"

