msgid "6400:[name]梨深[line]「イヤだよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]梨深[line]No...[%p]"

msgid "6500:はっきりと、拒否された。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:Rimi rejected my offer.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]梨深[line]「あたし……行きたくない」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]梨深[line]I don't want to go.[%p]"

msgid "6700:まさかそう言われるとは思いもよらなかった僕は、自分の耳を疑う。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:I'd never thought she'd refuse. I couldn't believe what I was hearing.[%p]"

msgid "6800:今まで、梨深は僕のワガママをなんでも聞いてくれた。[linebreak]いつも、僕を助けてくれた。僕を支えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:Rimi had always done whatever I'd wanted. She'd always been there to help me. She'd always been there to support me.[%p]"

msgid "6900:だから無条件に、なにを言っても肯定してくれるって思ってた。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:So, I'd thought she'd say yes to whatever I asked.[%p]"

msgid "7000:でも、そもそも拒否されるはずがないって思い込んでいた僕の方が異常なんだと、考え直す。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:But I realized now that I was silly for thinking she'd always say yes.[%p]"

msgid "7100:僕は、調子に乗ってたんだ。[linebreak]梨深に、甘えすぎていたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:I'd been arrogant. I'd treated her like a tool.[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]拓巳[line]「そう……」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]拓巳[line]I see.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]梨深[line]「それに――」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]梨深[line]And...[%p]"

msgid "7400:梨深は僕に背を向ける。[linebreak]そして自分自身を抱きしめるようにした。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:Rimi turned away from me. She wrapped her arms tight around her body.[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]梨深[line]「それに、タクも、行かない方がいい」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]梨深[line]You shouldn't go back, either.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]拓巳[line]「それって、どういう……」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]拓巳[line]What do you mean?[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]梨深[line]「実家には、戻らないで」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]梨深[line]Don't go home.[%p]"

msgid "7800:きっぱりとした口調。[linebreak]まるで命令されているような。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:Her voice was clear and unhesitating. Like she was giving me an order.[%p]"

msgid "7900:僕は戸惑う。[linebreak]梨深がどういう意図でそう言うのか理解できない。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:I didn't understand. I didn't know what would make her say that.[%p]"

msgid "8000:今、梨深はどんな顔をしているんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:What look was on her face right now?[%p]"

msgid "8100:分からない……。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:I didn't understand.[%p]"

msgid "8200:[name]拓巳[line]「わ、訳が、分からな――」[%p]"
msgstr "8200:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't understand.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]梨深[line]「あなたはなにも知らなくていい」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]梨深[line]You don't need to know anything.[%p]"

msgid "8400:その声音には、切迫感があった。[linebreak]ついさっきまでの梨深とはまるで別人だ。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:There was a tension in her voice. A sense of urgency. She was like a totally different person than she'd been before.[%p]"

msgid "8500:[name]梨深[line]「ここで、このコンテナハウスだけでずっと生きていけばいいの」[%p]"
msgstr "8500:[name]梨深[line]Just stay here in your room forever.[%p]"

msgid "8600:[name]梨深[line]「そうしてもらわないと……困るんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "8600:[name]梨深[line]I... need you to do that.[%p]"

msgid "8700:困る……？[%p]"
msgstr "8700:She needed me to do that?[%p]"

msgid "8800:っていうか、これは妄想……だよね？[linebreak]違う……の？[%p]"
msgstr "8800:Wait... this was a delusion, right? Right?[%p]"

