msgid "9000:甲高い音が耳に突き刺さった。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:A high-pitched sound stabbed my ears.[%p]"

msgid "9100:それはまるで、女性の悲鳴のような――[%p]"
msgstr "9100:It was like a girl's scream.[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]梨深[line]「それって」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]梨深[line]Does that mean...[%p]"

msgid "9300:梨深は難しい顔をして考え込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Rimi seemed lost in thought.[%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]梨深[line]「もしかして、ご、ご両親に紹介する、みたいな流れ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]梨深[line]Y-You're going to introduce me to your parents?[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "9600:梨深があまりにバカなことを言い出したから、思わずポカーンとしてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Rimi said something so ridiculous, my mouth fell open.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]梨深[line]「だとしたら心の準備がまだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]梨深[line]I need a little more time before I'm ready.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]拓巳[line]「ち、ちがっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]拓巳[line]N-No...[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]拓巳[line]「そうじゃなくて……」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]拓巳[line]Not like that.[%p]"

msgid "10000:突如――[%p]"
msgstr "10000:And suddenly...[%p]"

msgid "10100:甲高い音が耳に突き刺さった。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:A high-pitched sound stabbed my ears.[%p]"

msgid "10200:それはまるで、女性の悲鳴のような――[%p]"
msgstr "10200:It was like a girl's scream.[%p]"

msgid "10300:[name]梨深[line]「……！？」[%p]"
msgstr "10300:[name]梨深[line]...?![%p]"

msgid "10400:風が激しく吹き荒れ、[linebreak]空気が震え、[%p]"
msgstr "10400:The wind blew hard. The air shook around me.[%p]"

msgid "10500:真紅の輝きが視界を奪う。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:A crimson light blinded me.[%p]"

msgid "10600:なにが起こったのか分からないまま、僕は光の方へと顔を向ける。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:I turned toward the source of the light, unsure of what was going on.[%p]"

msgid "10700:コンテナハウスの上。[linebreak]見上げれば、そこに。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:There, on top of the shipping crate. I looked up...[%p]"

msgid "10800:ディソードを持った、蒼井セナの姿。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:And saw Sena Aoi holding her Di-Sword in her hand.[%p]"

msgid "10900:光の正体は、ディソードの明滅。[linebreak]だけど妙だ。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:The light was coming from the flashing Di-Sword. But something was strange.[%p]"

msgid "11000:前に見たときは、セナのディソードは、青い光を放っていたはずなのに。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:The last time I saw it, Sena's Di-Sword had been flashing with a blue light.[%p]"

msgid "11100:音はすぐに消え失せる。[linebreak]風もやむ。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:The sound quickly disappeared. The wind stopped.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]セナ[line]「答えろ――」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]セナ[line]Answer me.[%p]"

msgid "11300:鋭い声。[linebreak]冷たい視線。[linebreak]セナの瞳に浮かぶのは、明確な敵意。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Her voice was sharp. Her gaze was cold. I could see murder in her eyes.[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]セナ[line]「これを書いたのは、お前か？」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]セナ[line]Were you the one who wrote this?[%p]"

msgid "11500:そう言って突き出したのは、あの『Ｉｒ２』の落書きがされた作文用紙だった。[linebreak]なぜかしわくちゃになっている。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:She was holding the essay with the “Ir2” equation scribbled on the back. It was all wrinkled, like someone had crumpled it up.[%p]"

msgid "11600:どうして、セナがあれを持っているんだ。[linebreak]どうして、セナがここにいるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:Why would Sena have that? Why would she even be here?[%p]"

msgid "11700:不法侵入。[linebreak]その言葉が頭に浮かび。[linebreak]自分の部屋を物色されたことに気付く。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:The words “breaking and entering” came into my mind, and I realized that she'd been in my room.[%p]"

msgid "11800:どういうつもりだ？[%p]"
msgstr "11800:But why?[%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]セナ[line]「答えろと言っている」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]セナ[line]I told you to answer me.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そう、だけど……だから？」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]拓巳[line]Y-Yes, but... so what?[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃん！」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]梢[line]Takumi![%p]"

msgid "12200:今のはこずぴぃの心の声だ。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:Now it was Kozupii's voice.[%p]"

msgid "12300:彼女はセナの背後にいた。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:She was behind Sena's back.[%p]"

msgid "12400:セナの足にしがみつくようにして、こっちに顔を突き出している。その表情はやけに切迫していて――[%p]"
msgstr "12400:She was clinging to Sena's leg, and poking her head out at me. Her expression was incredibly tense.[%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]梢[line]「逃げるの！」[%p]"
msgstr "12500:[name]梢[line]Run![%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]拓巳[line]「え……？」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "12700:こずぴぃが叫ぶのとほぼ同時に、[linebreak]セナがその場から跳んでいた。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:Just as Kozupii shouted, Sena jumped.[%p]"

msgid "12800:剣を振りかぶり、[%p]"
msgstr "12800:She raised the sword...[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]梨深[line]「危ないっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]梨深[line]Watch out![%p]"

msgid "13000:梨深に腕を強く引かれ、僕は後ろ向きに倒れ込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:Rimi yanked me hard, and I fell backwards.[%p]"

msgid "13100:とっさに顔を上げ、それまで自分が立っていた場所を見る。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:I looked up at the place where I'd just been standing.[%p]"

msgid "13200:セナの剣が、屋上の床を抉っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Sena's sword had torn a chunk out of the ground.[%p]"

msgid "13300:すさまじいまでの、そして現実離れした切れ味と破壊力。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:Its sharpness and destructive power were almost unreal.[%p]"

msgid "13400:コンクリートを砕くほどの衝撃だったのに、剣の方には傷ひとつない。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:The impact had been enough to shatter concrete, but the blade was unharmed.[%p]"

msgid "13500:ディソードは、人に見えず、[linebreak]触れることさえできない剣じゃなかったの！？[%p]"
msgstr "13500:I thought the Di-Swords were supposed to be invisible, and you couldn't even touch them![%p]"

msgid "13600:僕の脳裏を、ある言葉がよぎった。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:Then I remembered what I'd heard before.[%p]"

msgid "13700:あの剣は、リアルブートされている――[%p]"
msgstr "13700:The sword must have been real booted.[%p]"

msgid "13800:この場にいる４人の周囲共通認識となったセナのディソードは、妄想ではなく現実。[linebreak]実際に人を斬ることができる大剣。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:The four of us here had a shared awareness of Sena's Di-Sword. It wasn't a delusion anymore. It was real. It was a huge sword with the power to cut someone in half.[%p]"

msgid "13900:もし梨深に引っ張ってもらわなかったら。[linebreak]僕はあの美しい剣に頭からキレイにスライスされ。[linebreak]即死だった。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:If Rimi hadn't pulled me back, the beautiful blade would've sliced into me, head first, and I'd have died instantly.[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あ、あああ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]拓巳[line]Aah... Aaah...[%p]"

msgid "14100:震えが全身を駆け巡る。[linebreak]セナは今、間違いなく僕を、[linebreak]殺そうとした――[%p]"
msgstr "14100:My whole body started to shake. Sena had just tried to... kill me.[%p]"

msgid "14200:どうして。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:Why?[%p]"

msgid "14300:頭の中が疑問でいっぱいになる。[linebreak]この前は、こずぴぃも入れて３人で一緒に、ガルガリ君を食べた。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:My mind was filled with questions. Not too long ago, she, Kozupii, and I had all been eating Garugari-kun popsicles together.[%p]"

msgid "14400:確かに僕らは友達と呼べるほどの仲じゃなかったし、この前だって最後まで怖い態度のままだったけど。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:We certainly weren't close enough that I could call her a friend, and she'd still scared me.[%p]"

msgid "14500:それでも、いきなりディソードで襲われるような、険悪な関係じゃなかったはず――[%p]"
msgstr "14500:But it certainly didn't feel like she was going to attack me on sight with a Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]セナ[line]「殺して……やる」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]セナ[line]I'm going to kill you.[%p]"

msgid "14700:セナが顔を上げ。[linebreak]なおも僕をにらみつけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:Sena looked up, glaring at me.[%p]"

msgid "14800:その動きは速かった。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:She moved fast.[%p]"

msgid "14900:あんな巨大な剣を持っているにもかかわらず。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Even though she was carrying that huge weapon,[%p]"

msgid "15000:短距離走のクラウチングスタートのように、地面を蹴り。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:she got into a crouch like a sprinter at the starting line, and began to run.[%p]"

msgid "15100:剣の切っ先を、地面に擦らせるようにして振り回して。[linebreak]僕への距離を詰めながら、上段の構えへ。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:The tip of the blade tore into the ground as she got closer and closer, and when she was close enough, she raised it high above her head.[%p]"

msgid "15200:本能が、一瞬で状況を悟る。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:My instincts told me in an instant what was going on.[%p]"

msgid "15300:本気だ。[linebreak]セナは、本気だ――[%p]"
msgstr "15300:She was serious. Sena was serious.[%p]"

msgid "15400:[name]拓巳[line]「わあああああ――」[%p]"
msgstr "15400:[name]拓巳[line]Waaah![%p]"

msgid "15500:僕は無様に仰向けに倒れたまま。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I was lying on the ground, staring up, helpless and pathetic.[%p]"

msgid "15600:絶叫する。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I screamed.[%p]"

msgid "15700:逃げられない。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:I couldn't escape.[%p]"

msgid "15800:あまりにも理不尽。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:This was just so unfair.[%p]"

msgid "15900:あまりにも突然。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:So sudden.[%p]"

msgid "16000:これでゲームオーバーなんて。[linebreak]必死で『将軍』から逃げてきた結果が、セナによる奇襲なんて。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:How could it suddenly be game over like this? All that time I'd spent running away from Shogun... And now I'd die to a surprise attack from Sena.[%p]"

msgid "16100:イヤだ――[linebreak]死にたくない――[%p]"
msgstr "16100:No... I don't want to die...[%p]"

msgid "16200:死にたくないよぉ！[%p]"
msgstr "16200:I don't want to die![%p]"

msgid "16300:[name]梨深[line]「――っ」[%p]"
msgstr "16300:[name]梨深[line]...![%p]"

msgid "16400:そこへ――[%p]"
msgstr "16400:And then...[%p]"

msgid "16500:ひとつの人影が飛び込んできて。[linebreak]僕とセナとの間に立ちはだかった。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:Someone leapt between us, standing between me and Sena.[%p]"

msgid "16600:見れば、その背中は梨深のもので。[linebreak]僕に迫り来るセナの行く手を塞ぐように、両手を広げている。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I realized it was Rimi. She was standing between me and Sena, with her arms spread out wide to block her path.[%p]"

msgid "16700:身を挺して、僕を庇ってくれるの……？[%p]"
msgstr "16700:Was she putting herself in danger to protect me?[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]セナ[line]「どけっ」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]セナ[line]Move.[%p]"

msgid "16900:でも、これじゃ梨深が死んじゃうよ……！[linebreak]そんなのイヤだ……！[%p]"
msgstr "16900:But Rimi... you'll die! I don't want that![%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]梢[line]「咲畑しゃんには、気をつけて」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]梢[line]You should be careful around Sakihata.[%p]"

msgid "17100:ふと。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Suddenly...[%p]"

msgid "17200:こずぴぃに以前言われた言葉を思い出した。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:I remembered what Kozupii had said before.[%p]"

msgid "17300:梨深の広げた両手に、淡い光が溢れ出す――[%p]"
msgstr "17300:Pale light began to pour out from between Rimi's spread arms.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]梢[line]「咲畑しゃんは、よく分かんないのら……」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]梢[line]I don't really understand her, nora.[%p]"

msgid "17500:梨深は――[%p]"
msgstr "17500:Rimi...[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]梨深[line]「タクに、手を出さないで」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]梨深[line]Leave Taku alone.[%p]"

msgid "17700:溢れた光を束ねるように、両手を重ね合わせて。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:...brought her hands together around the streaming rays of light.[%p]"

msgid "17800:空気が震えた。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:The air shook around us.[%p]"

msgid "17900:どこから出てきたのか、[linebreak]キラキラと輝く光の羽根が、[linebreak]梨深の周囲を舞う。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:Shining feathers of light appeared from out of nowhere and began to dance around Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "18000:彼女の手に現れたそれは――[%p]"
msgstr "18000:And in her hands, I saw...[%p]"

msgid "18100:[name]セナ[line]「なん……だと……」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]セナ[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "18200:勢いよく振り下ろしたセナの巨大なディソードを、難なく受け止めていた。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:Sena had brought her huge Di-Sword down with full force, but she easily blocked it.[%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]梨深[line]「タクを、追い詰めないで」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]梨深[line]Don't push him any closer to the edge.[%p]"

msgid "18400:それは、剣と呼ぶには、[linebreak]あまりに優美で。[linebreak]あまりに神々しく。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:The thing in her hands was far too elegant... far too holy... to be called a sword.[%p]"

msgid "18500:天使の翼かと見紛うほどだ――[%p]"
msgstr "18500:It was like the wings of an angel.[%p]"

msgid "18600:そして僕は理解した。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:And then I understood.[%p]"

msgid "18700:彼女も、[linebreak]咲畑梨深も……[%p]"
msgstr "18700:She... Rimi Sakihata...[%p]"

msgid "18800:ギガロマニアックスだという事実を。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:was also a Gigalomaniac.[%p]"

